            . I was in <placeName id="t18160529-40-crimeloc210">Newgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18160529-40-crimeloc210" type="placeName" value="Newgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18160529-40-crimeloc210" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160529-40-off208 t18160529-40-crimeloc210"></join>, on the 18th of May, at about twelve o'clock in the forenoon; I was coming from the West End of the Town to the City, and felt a crowd pressing on me; I turned round, and saw my handkerchief drop from the prisoner Myers, upon which the little boy picked it up, and concealed it under his coat. I took them both, and gave them in charge to an officer.</p>
               <p>
            
